---

<Base title="金融行业深度解析" description="投行、PE、VC、对冲基金、资产管理、商业银行、证券研究、量化——金融行业8大方向全景解析，中美职场对比">

  <a href="/industry/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-stone-400 hover:text-columbia-navy text-xs transition-colors no-underline mb-10 group">
    <span class="group-hover:-translate-x-0.5 transition-transform inline-block">←</span>
    行业解析
  </a>

  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="mb-12 pb-10 border-b border-stone-200">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
      <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] bg-amber-50 text-amber-700 border border-amber-200 font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Finance</span>
      <span class="text-[10px] text-stone-400 uppercase tracking-widest">8 个细分方向</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-stone-900 leading-tight mb-5">
      金融行业深度解析
    </h1>
    <p class="text-stone-500 leading-loose text-[0.9375rem] max-w-2xl mb-6">
      金融是最多文商科学生向往的方向，也是最容易"看起来懂、实际不懂"的行业。这里不是招聘广告，而是一个从业者视角的完整拆解——每个方向的历史、商业逻辑、真实日常、中美差异和未来走向。
    </p>

    <!-- Quick stats -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
      {[
        { label: '细分方向', value: '8个' },
        { label: '覆盖市场', value: '美国 + 中国' },
        { label: '薪酬数据', value: '2024-2025' },
        { label: '内容来源', value: '公开数据 + 论坛' },
      ].map(s => (
        <div class="bg-stone-50 border border-stone-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-center">
          <div class="font-bold text-columbia-navy text-lg">{s.value}</div>
          <div class="text-stone-400 text-xs mt-0.5">{s.label}</div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Overview: Finance ecosystem -->
  <section class="mb-14">
    <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-stone-900 mb-5">先看懂金融行业的全局地图</h2>
    <div class="bg-stone-50 border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl p-6 text-sm text-stone-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
      <p>金融行业最常见的误解，是把它当作一个整体。实际上，<strong class="text-stone-800">一级市场和二级市场是完全不同的生意</strong>，买方和卖方的利益结构截然不同，投行分析师和对冲基金分析师虽然名字相近，工作内容可能差10万八千里。</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-4">
        <div class="bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-xl p-4">
          <p class="font-semibold text-stone-800 mb-2">卖方（Sell-Side）</p>
          <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed">投资银行、证券经纪、卖方研究。<strong>为客户提供服务收取费用</strong>——承销IPO收承销费，撮合M&A收顾问费，写研究报告吸引机构客户交佣金。</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-stone-400 mt-2">代表机构：Goldman Sachs, Morgan Stanley, 国内头部券商</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-xl p-4">
          <p class="font-semibold text-stone-800 mb-2">买方（Buy-Side）</p>
          <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed"><strong>用自己管理的资金直接投资赚钱</strong>——PE/VC买未上市公司股权，对冲基金做多空套利，资管公募买股票债券。</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-stone-400 mt-2">代表机构：Blackstone, Bridgewater, 高瓴, 景林资产</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-stone-400 pt-2">💡 一般认为买方地位更高（直接管钱），但卖方（尤其是顶级投行）是进入买方的主要跳板——很多PE要求IB背景。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Sector cards -->
  <section>
    <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-stone-900 mb-6">8 个细分方向</h2>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
      {sectors.map((s) => (
        <a href={s.href} class="group block rounded-2xl border border-stone-200 bg-white p-6 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all no-underline">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
            <span class="text-3xl">{s.emoji}</span>
            <span class={`text-[10px] font-semibold px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full border ${s.diffColor}`}>
              入行难度：{s.difficulty}
            </span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-stone-900 text-lg mb-0.5 group-hover:text-columbia-navy transition-colors">{s.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-[11px] text-stone-400 mb-3">{s.titleEn}</p>
          <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">{s.desc}</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mb-4">
            {s.tags.map(t => (
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-amber-50 text-amber-700 border border-amber-200 font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">{t}</span>
            ))}
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 text-xs text-stone-500 pt-3 border-t border-stone-100">
            <span>🇺🇸 {s.salary_us}</span>
            <span>🇨🇳 {s.salary_cn}</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Disclaimer -->
  <div class="mt-12 bg-stone-50 border border-stone-200 rounded-xl px-5 py-4 text-xs text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">
    ⚠️ 薪酬数据来源于 Wall Street Oasis、Glassdoor、知乎、脉脉等公开平台，仅供参考。中国区数据已做模糊化处理，实际薪酬因机构、年份、个人背景差异较大。
  </div>
</Base>
